title: 'Furthermore, {} can be used to pattern match on the left hand side, i.e. {var = pat} gets an implicit variable and attempts to pattern match on “pat”; For example:'
pid: 6bc58a5f-446a-4080-82b5-91ccece8a2ac
body: |2-

  isEmpty : Vect n a -> Bool
  isEmpty {n = Z} _   = True
  isEmpty {n = S k} _ = False
